                        <button class="accordion-button" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#q1">How fresh are your dairy products?</button>
                    </h2>
                    <div id="q1" class="accordion-collapse collapse show" data-bs-parent="#faqAcc">
                        <div class="accordion-body">
                            We source directly from our partner farms daily, chill immediately, and maintain a cold chain until delivery.
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="accordion-item mint-card mt-3">
                    <h2 class="accordion-header">
                        <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#q2">Do you test for quality?</button>
                    </h2>
                    <div id="q2" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#faqAcc">
                        <div class="accordion-body">
                            Yes—each batch is lab-tested for purity and safety. We reject anything below standard.
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="accordion-item mint-card mt-3">
                    <h2 class="accordion-header">
                        <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#q3">What areas do you deliver to?</button>
                    </h2>
                    <div id="q3" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#faqAcc">
                        <div class="accordion-body">
                            We currently deliver across Dhaka city. More areas rolling out soon.
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="accordion-item mint-card mt-3">
                    <h2 class="accordion-header">
                        <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#q4">Can I cancel or change my order?</button>
                    </h2>
                    <div id="q4" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#faqAcc">
                        <div class="accordion-body">
                            Yes—contact support within 30 minutes of placing your order for changes or cancellations.
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- ===== REFUND & POLICY ===== -->
<section id="RefundPolicy" class="container py-5">
    <h2 class="section-title anchor-target text-center">Refund & Policy</h2>
    <div class="row g-4">
        <div class="col-12 col-lg-6">
            <div class="mint-card p-4 h-100">
                <h5 class="fw-bold mb-2">Refund Policy</h5>
                <ul class="list-check mb-0">
                    <li>Full refund for damaged/expired products reported within 24 hours.</li>
                    <li>Refunds processed via original payment method within 5–7 business days.</li>
                    <li>For cash-on-delivery, refunds are issued as store credit or bank transfer.</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-12 col-lg-6">
            <div class="mint-card p-4 h-100">
                <h5 class="fw-bold mb-2">Return Policy</h5>
                <ul class="list-check mb-0">
                    <li>Chilled items are returnable only upon delivery if seal is broken or package damaged.</li>
                    <li>Non-perishable items accept returns within 7 days if unopened and in original condition.</li>
                    <li>Please keep receipt and unboxing video/photos for claims.</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>


